Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration of 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Maximum time to achieve 'Completed + Resolved' from case start
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C23051D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration difference between 'Completed + Resolved' and 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + Resolved' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average lead time to 'Completed + Resolved' from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Earliest start time of 'Completed + Resolved' after 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Latest finish time of 'Completed + Resolved' before 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total elapsed time between first 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with high impact
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Maximum duration of 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with low impact
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C23051D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Resolved' filtered by the function ma == 'low' where ma is the last value of impact
